","tid":118274,"uid":11782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"我都要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次剝晒4隻同兩隻多生齒 <br />\n之後幾個星期辛苦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a8d219abec919f7a964941939d15a532ee302b","tid":118274,"uid":69417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"幾錢架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722b81778086a76d0bcfb92c55ff4472fa5f8ed0","tid":118274,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"點解價錢可以相差咁遠<br />\n打死都唔上大陸做"},{"pid":"b9b320b21a692493e69658771ade7d8f27f32262","tid":118274,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>～5萬蚊<br />\n今年價<br />\n醫院做一定係口腔恰面專科<br />\n麻醉師<br />\n手術室<br />\n全部都係錢</blockquote><br />\n點先知醫生點幫我安排<br />\n利申公家醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公立醫院都要咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府醫院剝一隻大約幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n冇錢就搵菲臘牙科，之前d巴打話幾十至幾百搞店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望一望個價目表<br />\nRemoval of Wisdom Tooth 拔除智慧齒 $5,000 - $10,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7421ca3ad61f5becd257de2763da5835269cfb","tid":118274,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"洗撚麻醉 <br />\n生剝咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f056666a3d17d328a9ba496f767d420d8d26d44","tid":118274,"uid":57276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"太近神經線要全麻<br />\n如果唔小心整傷神經線，<br />\n有可能會影響味覺、面部神經<br />\n<br />\n利申，乜都唔識，之前剝記得醫生講過"},{"pid":"878d54f6b97ebd315a7cfe5c88af8120722527d9","tid":118274,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"應該唔到病人去決定要唔要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f26316d88788de7a7ea044c54bc253b5e7e8b1","tid":118274,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"睇過兩個醫生都話要$6000一隻<br />\n因為打斜生又太近神經線 要專科搞<br />\n最後睇多個牙醫係青衣 $2xxx搞掂<br />\n傷口仲好細 過程又唔係好痛<br />\n但最神奇係唔洗consult<br />\n我一去就話剝 驚到仆街<br />\n而家仲有另一隻未剝<br />\n不過已經唔想再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf769e098c197fd1dfd4168c7d5522fdf89f3f3","tid":118274,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全麻應該做唔到<br />\n全身麻醉你個口會插左條喉 去幫助你呼吸 <br />\n你個口封實晒又點做手術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，全麻剝3隻智慧齒+犬齒<br />\n工作關係唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞓一晚醫院，第日照去飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一次過剝咁多隻 <br />\n第2日都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔痛?<br />\n近唔近神經線?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一日痛，但必理痛搞得掂<br />\n第二日已經好好多<br />\n有一隻近神經線<br />\n唔想分開兩次剝，全麻瞓個覺一次過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f7e63a7af4a3f31444c29599b39290fdc18a11","tid":118274,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該唔到病人去決定要唔要全身麻醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同政府醫生講要全麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職員先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e305d891f5560d4fc0d97c1fe7031c551d3d526c","tid":118274,"uid":28892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"好彩我打直生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩千一隻"},{"pid":"f32df8bf81899c6a849d0d84d98517d4826c692a","tid":118274,"uid":37595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誇咩張  我就係例子<br />\n將7-8年前做 <br />\n4隻智慧齒 打橫生係牙肉 入面 仲要貼神經線<br />\n私家坐底3-4萬 不過當時唔影響生活 排政府<br />\n唔夠一個月就叫我去瑪麗做全身麻醉 訓著之前<br />\n仲見到成班牙科生入黎做埋研究學習 <br />\n最後比左一千幾百 政府醫院錢就出院</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個月咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83706b4f0c9490a09b4ef41f977271e805969299","tid":118274,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"我估有啲位近骨麻醉唔到先要全身麻<br />\n係台灣剝，FEEL到佢切開左我啲肉之後個醫生同我講跟住個位近骨會有啲痛，<br />\nHI又痺又痛又肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866c6f9a7641d28d4710eec4504dd4f020ddc71b","tid":118274,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我估有啲位近骨麻醉唔到先要全身麻<br />\n係台灣剝，FEEL到佢切開左我啲肉之後個醫生同我講跟住個位近骨會有啲痛，<br />\nHI又痺又痛又肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd255501e8d7693dc4c1fa0da20254aad68eaf65","tid":118274,"uid":34025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過兩個醫生都話要$6000一隻<br />\n因為打斜生又太近神經線 要專科搞<br />\n最後睇多個牙醫係青衣 $2xxx搞掂<br />\n傷口仲好細 過程又唔係好痛<br />\n但最神奇係唔洗consult<br />\n我一去就話剝 驚到仆街<br />\n而家仲有另一隻未剝<br />\n不過已經唔想再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n青衣個個係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159aba4b7764cb7bac2f044ef9ac84238b5d2cb1","tid":118274,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我估有啲位近骨麻醉唔到先要全身麻<br />\n係台灣剝，FEEL到佢切開左我啲肉之後個醫生同我講跟住個位近骨會有啲痛，<br />\nHI又痺又痛又肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠麻醉藥"},{"pid":"d6c3dfbb6295dea3e39c428f882cfbcaf7d2f7c1","tid":118274,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"全身麻醉 會蠢個喎<br />\n有人同我講佢自己試過2次<br />\n佢個人真係好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56119d5dd35b2ced7df68aa11636026a3d45656b","tid":118274,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"係咪上年年尾ge我開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd牙生得衰    4隻都要剝   <br />\n其中一隻太近神經唔敢剝<br />\n<br />\n私家要～$4500 一隻  <br />\n其他洗牙藥費另計<br />\n<br />\n專科～$8000一隻<br />\n冇全身麻醉<br />\n<br />\n菲臘收左我仲等緊<br />\n$45<br />\n<br />\n真係痛等唔切<br />\n建議你搵搵土瓜灣高如春<br />\n手勢幾好   冇乜腫   第二日已經照常食野<br />\ntotal連藥xray好似$3500"},{"pid":"a84beacfb0c2763523ddcc0d1257c32efe490f93","tid":118274,"uid":48006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"其實我都係橫生 依家無痛..<br />\n<br />\n但長遠黎講係咪都要剝？"},{"pid":"e51469fb5f896578333fe03bab0b5ea0ac84bd83","tid":118274,"uid":48006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都係橫生 依家無痛..<br />\n<br />\n但長遠黎講係咪都要剝？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要既話係咪依家排定政府或者菲xx牙科？"},{"pid":"316ce2ca99cfd99cb8059cfa8d566a52aec7cf24","tid":118274,"uid":21091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"樓下牙醫剝<br />\n好似3000-4000一隻<br />\n我分兩次剝<br />\n每次兩隻<br />\n唔洗全麻"},{"pid":"e4cfaaf59c66f970b052b25846921c6fed465e82","tid":118274,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"屌見到標題笑到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbc08f5bbb085e156c2e54c4e89cec6f8aaac61","tid":118274,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"剝兩隻大牙呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a0feb5738173cb06f8aaef03b626b674d394a1","tid":118274,"uid":83192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"灣仔克街華星附近有間牙醫幾好又平<br />\n之前剝過好似千幾搞掂 響灣仔ive同華星中間嘅地鋪黎<br />\n不過間野好細要打去book 好似叫蔡慶和"},{"pid":"977515ba1b9a11f85c5b0f92006daa1d0dfe97d5","tid":118274,"uid":67257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"學校mock<br />\n下面2隻横生<br />\n千幾蚊一隻<br />\n<br />\nmock完頭個日痛到食唔到野，講野講一粒字都會帶動到傷口<br />\n個日全日唔知有冇講過30句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps唔知有冇睇錯，mock個陣見到有用螺絲批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d0a7dbad14423460eacfdc72f27df42d8d0bd0","tid":118274,"uid":29358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>～5萬蚊<br />\n今年價<br />\n醫院做一定係口腔恰面專科<br />\n麻醉師<br />\n手術室<br />\n全部都係錢</blockquote><br />\n點先知醫生點幫我安排<br />\n利申公家醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公立醫院都要咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府醫院剝一隻大約幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n冇錢就搵菲臘牙科，之前d巴打話幾十至幾百搞店</blockquote><br />\n菲臘都係幫你響瑪麗 排期做<br />\n早幾年我都有一隻出左三隻未出<br />\n菲臘幫我排期，全身麻醉一次幫我剝晒四隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似瞓左兩晚醫院<br />\n錢就計番你瞓左幾日醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34729d097769bacadf0b031c12e44a531d26dc1","tid":118274,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪上年年尾ge我開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd牙生得衰    4隻都要剝   <br />\n其中一隻太近神經唔敢剝<br />\n<br />\n私家要～$4500 一隻  <br />\n其他洗牙藥費另計<br />\n<br />\n專科～$8000一隻<br />\n冇全身麻醉<br />\n<br />\n菲臘收左我仲等緊<br />\n$45<br />\n<br />\n真係痛等唔切<br />\n建議你搵搵土瓜灣高如春<br />\n手勢幾好   冇乜腫   第二日已經照常食野<br />\ntotal連藥xray好似$3500</blockquote><br />\n菲臘收病人有咩準則？"},{"pid":"7423a051e1b125323069c78823013fc40878a166","tid":118274,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"4月頭政府到剥<br />\n好驚阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36854b7b993e6b45ebfc34487233d1428c5fa4fd","tid":118274,"uid":51006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"留名等攻略"},{"pid":"e2e342f4f04b672dff0fe51a10ccc2ee62d7da93","tid":118274,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我估有啲位近骨麻醉唔到先要全身麻<br />\n係台灣剝，FEEL到佢切開左我啲肉之後個醫生同我講跟住個位近骨會有啲痛，<br />\nHI又痺又痛又肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠麻醉藥</blockquote><br />\n但係成半個口都麻晒，同埋真係佢話痛嗰陣先痛<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb05cea42ae111727467fb2b2bd48aa55493d2","tid":118274,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"成班未做過就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牙科保健未完？<br />\n利申，上年揾尖咀專科一次過四隻，一個鐘全麻，三皮之後0痛楚"},{"pid":"fbfe07cd09ed0422692dee9a2b15c640d0b716a1","tid":118274,"uid":11824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"深圳愛康健，800有找"},{"pid":"2aecb35ee04491945b723e8234c4fc726778ed9a","tid":118274,"uid":2536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"其實最恐怖係佢用個夾夾碎你啲牙再拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽住啲聲真係想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612f7d307000bd68cd9ec1abcb12416151f24d29","tid":118274,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"小學雞個時有隻牙向橫一隻向上生<br />\n要開刀拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛到me<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375fb240ed5c8bf14b7190dbd3e5697ddbf031ea","tid":118274,"uid":7229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"即係牙腳近神經線，如果全麻就唔會有面癱risk?<br />\n睇過大學牙醫話4 隻都打橫生近神經線有風險，而家又唔痛唔剩，係成日攝著野食要了牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfeb92a3b093e39edc6aa485c7971b91bd3cc14c","tid":118274,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a482c982b7b293188d51a22189e8bd4b214505f","tid":118274,"uid":10495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"4隻剝曬 分兩次做 每次兩隻對咬<br />\n45蚊+45蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160d0b02ff73181736609034f428a4037a7a1cbb","tid":118274,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas